OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely cloudy morning on
OL,6,FFriday but bright or sunny spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping at times. Cloudier by late
OL,8,Fafternoon with some patchy rain.
OL,9,FBreeze picking up.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FOften cloudy with further
OL,12,Foutbreaks of mostly light and patchy
OL,13,Fdrizzle during the evening.
OL,14,FStrengthening winds will herald a band
OL,15,Fof heavy rain later in the night.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FRain soon clearing to the
OL,18,Feast tomorrow with sunny spells and
OL,19,Fshowers following. These locally heavy
OL,20,Fwith hail and a risk of thunder.
OL,21,FRather breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
