OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FUnsettled on Sunday with a mixture of
OL,7,Fsunny spells and showers. Often cloudy
OL,8,FMonday and Tuesday, with few showers
OL,9,Fin the mix. Temperatures generally
OL,10,Fclose to average. Windy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
